# Development Workflow

## Getting Started

1. Install dependencies: `npm install`
2. Start development server: `npm run dev`

## Project Configuration

- [babel.config.js](mdc:babel.config.js) - Babel configuration
- [metro.config.js](mdc:metro.config.js) - Metro bundler configuration
- [.babelrc](mdc:.babelrc) - Additional Babel settings

## Supabase Integration

The app uses Supabase for backend services:
- Authentication
- Content storage (lessons, chapters)
- User progress tracking

## Type Generation

Generate Supabase types: `npm run generate:types`
